Resource Profile: The AuditEvent for a successful Brewed Hot Beverage

Defining URL:http://example.org/StructureDefinition/HotBeverage.Brewed
Version:2021-April-1st
Name:BrewedLog
Title:The AuditEvent for a successful Brewed Hot Beverage
Status:Active as of 2021-04-21T11:22:23-04:00
Definition:

An AuditEvent profile for when request to brew a Hot Beverage action happens successfully.

Source Resource:XML / JSON / Turtle

The official URL for this profile is: 

http://example.org/StructureDefinition/HotBeverage.Brewed
